name: Free Fire Max
dec: Free Fire MAX is an enhanced, standalone version of the popular battle royale game, offering an optimized experience with Ultra HD graphics and breathtaking effects. In each 10-minute match, 50 players parachute onto a deserted island to scavenge for weapons and supplies while fighting to be the last one standing. The game is supported by exclusive Firelink technology, allowing players to sync their progress with the original Free Fire and play all game modes together.

name: BGMI
dec: Battlegrounds Mobile India (BGMI) is a free-to-play, online multiplayer battle royale game developed and published by the South Korean company Krafton, exclusively for players in India. In the game, up to 100 players parachute onto an island, scavenge for weapons and gear, and fight to be the last person or team standing. It is a culturally localized version of PUBG Mobile that offers an immersive and competitive gaming experience with its own dedicated esports ecosystem and frequent updates.

name: Crisis Action
dec: Crisis Action is a popular free-to-play eSports first-person shooter (FPS) mobile game that features real-time, massive online multiplayer combat. It offers a wide variety of game modes, including classic team battles, bomb mode, death matches, and unique options like Mech mode and Zero Gravity. Players can collect and upgrade a vast arsenal of over 200 weapons and gear to compete in ranked matches or join clans with friends.

name: Call of Duty®
mname: Call of Duty®: Modern Warfare® II
dec: Call of Duty is a blockbuster military first-person shooter franchise published by Activision. The games feature cinematic single-player campaigns set across various historical and fictional conflicts, from World War II to modern and future warfare scenarios. The series is renowned for its fast-paced multiplayer combat and additional cooperative modes like the popular Zombies survival experiences and free-to-play battle royale modes like Warzone.

name: Warframe
dec: Warframe is a free-to-play, co-op, third-person action game set in a sprawling sci-fi universe. Players control Warframes  bio-mechanical suits with unique, powerful abilities and fast-paced parkour movement, to battle various enemy factions across the Origin System. The core gameplay involves completing missions, collecting a vast array of weapons and gear, and customizing everything through an extensive modding system.

name: Striker Zone
dec: Striker Zone is a free-to-play online multiplayer first-person shooter (FPS) game set in the Chernobyl exclusion zone. Players engage in dynamic PvP battles, including team matches and deathmatch mode, across various maps. The game features outstanding 3D graphics, a wide array of customizable weapons and armor, and the ability to join clans and participate in world tournaments.

name: Apex Legends
dec: Apex Legends is a free-to-play first-person hero shooter and battle royale game set in the Titanfall universe. Players choose from an ever-growing roster of Legends, each with unique abilities, to form three-person squads. The objective is to scavenge for weapons and gear, outlast all other teams on a constantly shrinking map, and be the last squad standing in the Apex Games.

name: The Sims 4
dec: The Sims 4 is a life simulation game that empowers players to create and control virtual people, called Sims. The game offers powerful creative tools to design unique Sims with distinct personalities and emotions, and to build and furnish their dream homes. Players then direct the lives of their Sims, exploring vibrant neighborhoods, building relationships, pursuing careers, and telling engaging, open-ended stories

name: Lostark
dec: Lost Ark is a free-to-play, isometric MMO action role-playing game (ARPG) that combines deep RPG progression with a dynamic, hack-and-slash combat system. Players journey across the vast world of Arkesia, customizing their characters with diverse advanced classes and powerful skills, to battle demonic forces and colossal bosses in search of the fabled Lost Ark artifact. The game features a rich mix of content, including cinematic story quests, extensive exploration, deep endgame dungeons and raids, life skills like crafting, and both cooperative and competitive PvP modes.

name: Destiny 2
dec: Destiny 2 is an online-only, action-role-playing first-person shooter game where players assume the role of a Guardian, a protector of Earth's last safe city. Players journey across the solar system using powerful elemental abilities and unique weapons to battle various alien threats and uncover the mysteries of the Light and Darkness. The game features a rich, ongoing narrative with both single-player story campaigns and a variety of cooperative (raids, strikes) and competitive (PvP, Gambit) multiplayer modes.

name: forza horizon 5
dec: orza Horizon 5 is a racing video game set in a vibrant open world based on Mexico, where players lead expeditions in hundreds of customizable cars. It features a dynamic, evolving open world with a diverse map, including volcanoes, jungles, and ancient ruins, and hosts a variety of events, challenges, and multiplayer modes. Key features include a deep campaign with unique missions, weekly changing seasonal events, and social features like the Horizon Arcade for continuous, menu-free fun with friends.

name: MR RACER
dec: MR Racer Three is likely a colloquial name for the game MR RACER, a thrilling and challenging mobile car racing game developed by ChennaiGames Studio. It is known for its blend of online and offline gameplay modes, realistic 3D graphics, and extensive car customization options

name: Rush Rally 3
dec: Rush Rally 3 is a highly regarded, realistic rally simulation game available across mobile (iOS and Android), PC (Windows/macOS), and Nintendo Switch platforms. It is praised for offering a console-level experience with detailed physics and extensive content, developed primarily by a single person

name: RPG Antiquia Lost
dec: Premium RPG Antiquia Lost is an authentic, classic turn-based JRPG that follows a young man, Bine, and a unique slime heroine named Lunaria on a journey to uncover the truth behind mysterious disappearances in their world. The game features a deep character progression system where Lunaria grows stronger by eating gems and players can plant seeds to harvest stat-boosting items. With an emphasis on the power of trusting hearts and filled with classic RPG elements like weapon development and arenas, it delivers a nostalgic, easygoing experience for fans of the genre

name: The Hidden World
dec: Hiccup, now chief of Berk, has created a crowded yet peaceful dragon utopia. When a ruthless dragon hunter named Grimmel threatens their way of life, Hiccup and Toothless must journey to a mythical safe haven for dragons. In the process, they must both make difficult decisions about their destinies and what it means to let go in order to save their kind.

name: Pango Pirate
dec: Pango Pirate is a charming, open-ended adventure game for young children. Players join Pango on a treasure hunt, traveling the seas in his boat and exploring various islands. The game involves solving simple logic puzzles and riddles to find 21 unique treasures hidden across the world

name: Most Wanted
dec: A lone street racer arrives in Rockport, loses their prized BMW in a rigged race with the Blacklist gang leader, Razor, and is arrested by police sergeant Cross. After being released with the help of an undercover cop named Mia, the player must climb the Blacklist of 15 elite racers to exact revenge, recover their car, and eventually escape a massive police manhunt

name: Rush Rally 2
dec: Rush Rally 2 is a mobile rally racing simulator that offers a console-quality experience with authentic physics and car dynamics. Players can compete in World Rally Championships and Rallycross modes across 72 unique stages with varying surface types like snow, gravel, and dirt. The game features extensive car customization, real-time multiplayer, and diverse skill-based mini-games.

name: Batwheels Race
dec: Batwheels Race is a mobile racing game based on the animated children's TV series, available on platforms like Google Play. In the game, players must help the heroic Batwheels characters stop the villainous Legion of Zoom from cheating to win the annual Gotham Grand Prix. The core gameplay involves racing vehicles through various courses, avoiding traps set by the villains to ensure a fair victory.
